OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with some light
OL,6,Frain during the morning, especially in
OL,7,Fthe northwest and along southern
OL,8,Fcoastal districts. Becoming drier with
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells developing into
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Feeling warm and muggy.
OL,11,FLight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FExtensive low cloud with some
OL,14,Flight rain and drizzle along southern
OL,15,Fcoastal districts and hills overnight.
OL,16,FDrier and rather cloudy elsewhere. A
OL,17,Fwarm and muggy night. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
