OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,6,Fdrizzle, especially along southern
OL,7,Fcoastal districts and hills. Becoming
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter in the afternoon.
OL,9,FVery warm and humid. Chance of
OL,10,Fisolated thunderstorms by evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,13,Ffine with some sunshine. Turning very
OL,14,Fwarm or locally hot, and feeling humid
OL,15,Ftowards the weekend. Staying mainly
OL,16,Fdry, but with a small chance of
OL,17,Fthunderstorms.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
